@BASE_TR(ARGS)
#LOCALSIZE 1
#LOCALSSIZE 1
#FUNCTIONS
#DIMS DYNAMIC TR_RESULT
#DIMS DYNAMIC SAFE_NAME

SAFE_NAME '= REPLACE(ARGS, "'", "''")
TR_RESULT '= SQL_EXECUTE_SCALAR_STRING("TR_DB", @"SELECT v FROM CSV_MAP WHERE k = '%SAFE_NAME%';")
SIF TR_RESULT != ""
	RETURNF TR_RESULT
PRINTFORML ※未能找到%ARGS%翻译，请保存日志报错
RETURNF ARGS


